{"TopicId":189393,"ForumId":109,"TopicTitle":"The Importance of Quality Terrain Texturing","CreatedByName":"KSACheese","CreatedById":150877,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-10-29T19:33:52Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"KSACheese","CreatedById":150877,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-10-29T19:33:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAs the title implies, I believe it is extremely important that Star Theory keeps up the amazing work that SQUAD has done in the latest update with terrain shaders. In my personal experience, I have felt a greater drive to implement ground based operations in my latest career mode. This has brought up another factor in improving the lack of interactivity with ground operations. Specifically, I have spent more and more time on the surface of the Mun or Minmus doing rover missions or base operations simply because I no longer feel like I\u0027m landing on a grey mush.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNow, my highest hopes\u00A0are that Star Theory will continue this. With the addition of colonies and possibly expanding science and career mode, a high-quality ground scatter and ground texturing will be a great addition. Let me know how you guys feel about this as well!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"mcwaffles2003","CreatedById":180102,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-10-29T19:50:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBased on the rover in the reveal trailer jumping a gap and the final cut scene I think theyre paying attention here too\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"RealKerbal3x","CreatedById":183830,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-10-29T20:51:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI mean, this is only pre-alpha gameplay, but the Mun\u2019s terrain already looks pretty good:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022ksp2.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002251.79\u0022 height=\u0022530\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022 src=\u0022https://megagames.com/sites/default/files/game-content-images/ksp2.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u2019m sure it\u2019ll look even better than this when the game releases.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Snark","CreatedById":125662,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-10-30T01:03:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223696883\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022189393\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221572377632\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022150877\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022KSACheese\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n5 hours ago, KSACheese said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\na high-quality ground scatter and ground texturing will be a great addition.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes, they\u0027re putting a \u003Cem\u003E\u003Cu\u003Elot\u003C/u\u003E\u003C/em\u003E of effort into this, and it looks great.\u00A0 I think no worries there.\u00A0 They\u0027re clearly making this a priority.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"NoMrBond","CreatedById":69263,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-10-30T01:15:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223697081\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022189393\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221572397438\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022125662\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Snark\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n8 minutes ago, Snark said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes, they\u0027re putting a \u003Cem\u003E\u003Cu\u003Elot\u003C/u\u003E\u003C/em\u003E of effort into this, and it looks great.\u00A0 I think no worries there.\u00A0 They\u0027re clearly making this a priority.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPics or it didn\u0027t happen\u00A0 \u00A0 \u00A0 /s\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut seriously, hanging out for more KSP2 news/media\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"KerbolExplorer","CreatedById":177191,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-11-03T20:46:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223696950\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022189393\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221572382294\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022183830\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022RealKerbal3x\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 10/29/2019 at 8:51 PM, RealKerbal3x said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI mean, this is only pre-alpha gameplay, but the Mun\u2019s terrain already looks pretty good:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://megagames.com/sites/default/files/game-content-images/ksp2.jpg\u0022 title=\u0022Enlarge image\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022ksp2.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage ipsImage_thumbnailed\u0022 data-ratio=\u002251.79\u0022 height=\u0022530\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022 src=\u0022https://megagames.com/sites/default/files/game-content-images/ksp2.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u2019m sure it\u2019ll look even better than this when the game releases.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nyeah it looks pretty good but...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAm i the only one that thinks the terrain has really poor quality textures?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"RealKerbal3x","CreatedById":183830,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-11-03T20:50:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223699524\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022189393\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221572814015\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022177191\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022KerbolExplorer\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, KerbolExplorer said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nyeah it looks pretty good but...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAm i the only one that thinks the terrain has really poor quality textures?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAs I said, it is pre-alpha (so it\u2019ll probably improve by the actual release).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso,\u00A0I reckon Star Theory don\u2019t want the graphics of KSP2 to be upstaged by an update to the original game \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:wink:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:wink:\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Bej Kerman","CreatedById":182413,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-11-07T22:51:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223696950\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022189393\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221572382294\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022183830\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022RealKerbal3x\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 10/29/2019 at 8:51 PM, RealKerbal3x said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI mean, this is only pre-alpha gameplay, but the Mun\u2019s terrain already looks pretty good:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://megagames.com/sites/default/files/game-content-images/ksp2.jpg\u0022 title=\u0022Enlarge image\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022ksp2.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage ipsImage_thumbnailed\u0022 data-ratio=\u002251.79\u0022 height=\u0022530\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022 src=\u0022https://megagames.com/sites/default/files/game-content-images/ksp2.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u2019m sure it\u2019ll look even better than this when the game releases.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAll they have to do is make the rocks blend in more, and you\u0027ve got something 1000x better than KSP 1.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}